channel.title: Run server and compile error ?!
channel.description: :confused: i have project 16 source, if i hit compile or runserver on it, it says another program is currently using that file. i exited out of literally everything then tried and got the same thing... :confused:

item.title: Run server and compile error ?!
item.dc:creator: @jewsus987 jewsus987
item.description:
@jewsus987 wrote:

granty123:

Have you edited the compiler to what your java is set to? I cant remember what i put but check out the sections on making a server…

yea i put the compiler to:

echo off
title yourservernamehere
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe” server
pause

and it still says same thing =\
